{"tid":1576124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新戰線]雞蛋與高牆","createTime":"2019-09-17T06:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:50:04.000Z","uid":163271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"09e1502d3a3310dc1ad13f16271e5a88499b3f90","tid":1576124,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"利申 洗白撚，任屌唔嬲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/277129625984144/posts/913128755717558?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F277129625984144%2Fposts%2F913128755717558%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F4m5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=16bc05ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/277129625984144/posts/913128755717558?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府推警察出黎，佢地係第一幅牆<br />\n呢幅牆好硬，點打都打唔爛<br />\n但係如果呢幅牆<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>入面</strong></span><br />\n有一粒磚頭開始慢慢跌落黎<br />\n然後就會連帶埋其他磚頭一齊跌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁呢一幅牆就會訓低</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n重申 即管屌我 但我想贏呢場仗 所以求集思廣益點樣用呢條戰線<br />\n<br />\n推到有議員見到 我諗議員先可以大機會啲connect到呢班白警"},{"pid":"b68f82323c1bf7a65e7b40a1005578ca0b5a732c","tid":1576124,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"ab793fe6c2889745069a194807a2516e43cbaed7","tid":1576124,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor